for setup the testing step need to follow
1-> install the react testing library
2->install jest
3-> install babel
3-> add config babel config file babel.config.jest(
    this overide parcel babel file, parcel uses babel behind the schene so for disabling the 
    babel transpilation in parcel need to write the config parcel.rc(
        this config find on parcel official docs go parcel docs then go left side find the js 
        then click on it go right side and click babel and scroll down you find the other tool
        where you find the config of parcel
    )
)
final write the test = "jest" in script so you can use the cmd npm run test 
